FBIS3-37501 "drsov034_a_94006" FBIS-SOV-94-034 Document Type:Daily Report 18 Feb 1994 RUSSIA INTERNATIONAL AFFAIRS Grachev, U.S. Secretary Perry Discuss Bosnia on Phone LD1702181794 Moscow ITAR-TASS World Service in Russian 1749 GMT 17 Feb 94 LD1702181794 Moscow ITAR-TASS World Service Language: Russian Article Type:BFN [Text] Moscow, 17 Feb (ITAR-TASS) -- Ways of achieving a peaceful resolution of the Bosnian crisis were today the subject of a telephone conversation between Russian Defense Minister Pavel Grachev and U.S. Defense Secretary William Perry. The conversation, according to the Russian Defense Ministry Information and Press Directorate, took place via the recently established direct telephone line linking the two countries' military departments. The Directorate gave no details about the conversation.
